room_description: The year is 1930. You are a flashy, no-holds barred private detective during the height of prohibition in Chicago. Chicago is run by Al Capone, the most dangerous gangster in modern time. He is set for trial in one hour and it's up to you with the help of Elliott Ness to gather evidence to put him away for life.
